Summer By Espolòn⁠
⁠
Campari came to us with one clear and direct goal: to create social and digital content that can be shared throughout the summer, inviting new and existing consumers to enjoy a simple, yet wonderful range of products in a genuine seasonal fashion. Our job was to plant the seed of celebration by producing a simple, energetic, aspirational and relatable suite of visuals—video and stills—that celebrated two things. Espolòn Tequila & the summer.⁠
⁠

⁠
